snippet.title: Daniel Schmachtenberger:  Phase Shift for Humanity (clip)
snippet.description:
Daniel Schmachtenberger is a futurist, evolutionary philosopher and strategist, and social engineer.

The full conversation with David Fuller of Rebel Wisdom looks at the growing civilisation-level crisis that we are beginning to see around us, and looks at what a genuine 'phase shift' for human progress might look like: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nQRzxEobWco

Rebel Wisdom is a platform for the biggest ideas around. 
http://www.rebelwisdom.co.uk/
